Class and special pages have taken character data and separated it into probable builds. As such, the groupings and associated data will change over time to reflect what is currently accurate.

Looking at class and build pages, what you see and what it means:

Looking at skills you can assume that:

  • If the first number is 50%, then half of the characters fall into that "build"
  • If the percent bar following a skill is 100% then every character in that group has points in that skill
  • If the percent is 100% and the total points is high that skill is likely a main skill or synergy
  • If the percent is 100% but the total is low that skill is likely one-point-wonder like Hydra and Whirlwind or just a prerequisite
